=== 滅絕 ===
棲息於南美洲太平洋沿岸的海懶獸於上新世晚期絕種，在[[巴拿馬地峽|巴拿馬地峽]]的形成後改變了海流方向，因而造成南美洲沿太平洋岸水溫的下降，並使著海懶獸賴以為生的[[海草|海草]]大量滅絕。同時海懶獸的低新陳代謝速率使得牠們在低溫的海洋中較難以維持體溫<ref name="Amson2015">{{Cite journal|last= Amson|first= E.|last2= Argot|first2= C.|last3= McDonald|first3=H. G.|last4=de Muizon|first4= C.|year= 2015|title= Osteology and functional morphology of the axial postcranium of the marine sloth ''Thalassocnus'' (Mammalia, Tardigrada) with paleobiological implications|journal= Journal of Mammalian Evolution|volume= 22|issue= 4|pages= 473–518|doi= 10.1007/s10914-014-9280-7}}</ref>。

南美洲與北美洲的地懶大約於11,000年前現代人類出現時絕種，許多[[更新世巨型動物群|更新世巨型動物群]]也約於此時絕種。在南美洲與北美洲都曾經有發現地懶被人類殺害、烹煮、食用的相關證據<ref name="time-life"/>。[[第四纪冰河时期|末次冰河時期]]結束時所帶來的氣候變遷也可能是地懶滅絕的原因。

棲息於[[加勒比|加勒比]]地區的地懶直到5,000年前人類到來安地列斯群島後才絕種，遠晚於棲息於南北美大陸上的地懶<ref name="Steadman">{{cite journal|last=Steadman|first=D. W.|author2=Martin, P. S.|author3=MacPhee, R. D. E.|author4=Jull, A. J. T.|author5=McDonald, H. G.|author6=Woods, C. A.|author7=Iturralde-Vinent, M.|author8=Hodgins, G. W. L.|date=2005-08-16|title=Asynchronous extinction of late Quaternary sloths on continents and islands|journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences|Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. USA]]|volume=102|issue=33|pages=11763–11768|doi=10.1073/pnas.0502777102|pmc=1187974|pmid=16085711|author1link=David Steadman|author2link=Paul S. Martin}}</ref>。

==生物學==
[[File:Two-toed_sloth_Costa_Rica_-_cropped.jpg|thumb]]，攝於[[哥斯大黎加|哥斯大黎加]][[曼努埃爾安東尼奧國家公園|曼努埃爾安東尼奧國家公園]]]]

=== 外型 ===
樹懶體長約 {{convert|60|to|80|cm|abbr=on}}，體重約 {{convert|3.6|to|7.7|kg|abbr=on}}，二趾樹懶的體型較大<ref>{{cite web|title=Sloth|url=https://kids.nationalgeographic.com/animals/sloth/#sloth-beach-upside-down.jpg|website=National Geographic|accessdate=1 December 2017|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411125624/https://kids.nationalgeographic.com/animals/sloth/#sloth-beach-upside-down.jpg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。樹懶具有長手臂以及外耳不明顯的頭。三趾樹懶有一條長約 {{convert|5|to|6|cm|abbr=on}} 的尾巴。幾乎所有的哺乳動物均有7節[[頸椎|頸椎]]，二趾樹懶只有6節，而三趾樹懶則有9節<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Narita|first=Yuichi|last2=Kuratani|first2=Shigeru|date=2005-03-15|title=Evolution of the vertebral formulae in mammals: A perspective on developmental constraints|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/jez.b.21029/abstract|journal=Journal of Experimental Zoology Part B: Molecular and Developmental Evolution|language=en|volume=304B|issue=2|pages=91–106|doi=10.1002/jez.b.21029|issn=1552-5015|access-date=2018-10-25|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201232602/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/jez.b.21029/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref>，讓牠們得以270度轉動牠們的頭部<ref name="natgeo">{{cite web|title=Three-Toed Sloths|url=https://www.nationalgeographic.com/animals/mammals/group/three-toed-sloths/|website=National Geographic|accessdate=1 December 2017|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124054553/https://www.nationalgeographic.com/animals/mammals/group/three-toed-sloths/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 生理學 ===
樹懶具有有色視覺，但視力很差。樹懶的聽力也很差，主要依靠嗅覺與觸覺來尋找食物<ref name="bri">{{cite web|title=Sloth|url=https://www.britannica.com/animal/sloth|website=Encyclopedia Brittanica|accessdate=1 December 2017|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519141514/https://www.britannica.com/animal/sloth|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

樹懶擁有非常慢的[[代謝|代謝]]（低於同體型哺乳動物的 50%）及非常低的體溫，活動時體溫僅有{{convert|30|to|34|C|abbr=on}}，休息時則更低。樹懶為{{link-en|異溫|heterothermic}}動物，牠們的體溫會隨著周遭環境溫度而變化，範圍大約在 {{convert|25|to|35|C|abbr=on}}，但最低時可能只有 {{convert|20|C}}<ref name="bri" />。

樹懶毛髮的生長方向與其他哺乳動物相反，哺乳動物的毛髮生長一般由脊椎向四肢延伸，但由於樹懶多半倒吊於樹上，四肢位置多半高於軀幹，相反的毛髮生長方向讓這些毛髮得以維持順向並起到保護樹懶的作用。樹懶的毛髮上同時還長有共生性的藻類，能夠提供牠們[[偽裝|偽裝]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Suutari|first=Milla|last2=Majaneva|first2=Markus|last3=Fewer|first3=David P.|last4=Voirin|first4=Bryson|last5=Aiello|first5=Annette|last6=Friedl|first6=Thomas|last7=Chiarello|first7=Adriano G.|last8=Blomster|first8=Jaanika|date=2010-01-01|title=Molecular evidence for a diverse green algal community growing in the hair of sloths and a specific association with Trichophilus welckeri(Chlorophyta, Ulvophyceae)|journal=BMC Evolutionary Biology|volume=10|pages=86|doi=10.1186/1471-2148-10-86|issn=1471-2148|pmc=2858742|pmid=20353556}}</ref>，減少被[[美洲豹|美洲豹]]、[[豹貓|豹貓]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Moreno|first=Ricardo S.|last2=Kays|first2=Roland W.|last3=Samudio|first3=Rafael|date=2006-08-24|title=Competitive Release in Diets of Ocelot (Leopardus pardalis) and Puma (Puma concolor) after Jaguar (Panthera onca) Decline|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-mammalogy_2006-08_87_4/page/808|journal=Journal of Mammalogy|volume=87|issue=4|pages=808–816|doi=10.1644/05-MAMM-A-360R2.1|issn=0022-2372}}</ref>與[[角鵰|角鵰]]發現的機會<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Aguiar-Silva|first=F. Helena|last2=Sanaiotti|first2=Tânia M.|last3=Luz|first3=Benjamim B.|date=2014-03-01|title=Food Habits of the Harpy Eagle, a Top Predator from the Amazonian Rainforest Canopy|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=48|issue=1|pages=24–35|doi=10.3356/JRR-13-00017.1|issn=0892-1016}}</ref>。樹懶毛髮上也由於長有藻類，形成了獨特的小型生態系，棲息著許多種的[[片利共生|片利共生]]與[[寄生|寄生]]性[[節肢動物|節肢動物]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gilmore|first=D. P.|last2=Da Costa|first2=C. P.|last3=Duarte|first3=D. P. F.|date=2001-01-01|title=Sloth biology: an update on their physiological ecology, behavior and role as vectors of arthropods and arboviruses|journal=Brazilian Journal of Medical and Biological Research|volume=34|issue=1|pages=9–25|doi=10.1590/S0100-879X2001000100002|issn=0100-879X|pmid=11151024}}</ref>。寄生性的節肢動物包括會吸血的[[蚊|蚊]]、[[白蛉|白蛉]]、{{link-en|錐蝽亞科|Triatominae|錐蝽}}、[[蝨|蝨]]、[[蜱|蜱]]與[[蟎|蟎]]；而行片利共生的節肢動物則包括高度特化的[[甲蟲|甲蟲]]、蟎與[[蛾|蛾]]<ref name="Sloth arthropod biology">{{cite journal|last1=Gilmore|first1=D. P.|last2=Da Costa|first2=C. P.|last3=Duarte|first3=D. P. F.|year=2001|title=Sloth biology: an update on their physiological ecology, behavior and role as vectors of arthropods and arboviruses|url=http://www.scielo.br/pdf/bjmbr/v34n1/3877m.pdf|journal=Brazilian Journal of Medical and Biological Research|volume=34|issue=1|pages=9–25|doi=10.1590/S0100-879X2001000100002|issn=1678-4510|pmid=11151024|access-date=2020-03-23|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106160418/http://www.scielo.br/pdf/bjmbr/v34n1/3877m.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而這些節肢動物的糞便也能滋養藻類，使得樹懶能夠從中得利<ref>{{cite web|url=http://phenomena.nationalgeographic.com/2014/01/21/can-moths-explain-why-sloths-poo-on-the-ground/|title=Can Moths Explain Why Sloths Poo On the Ground?|author=Ed Yong|author-link=Ed Yong|work=Phenomena|date=2014-01-21|access-date=2020-03-23|archive-date=2018-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180529070736/http://phenomena.nationalgeographic.com/2014/01/21/can-moths-explain-why-sloths-poo-on-the-ground/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前有觀察到身上帶有大量節肢動物的物種包括：白喉三趾樹懶、褐喉三趾樹懶與二趾樹懶<ref name="Sloth arthropod biology" />。

=== 活動能力 ===
樹懶的四肢演化成適合吊掛以及抓握，而非支撐自身體重。肌肉只佔了總體重的25-30%，而其他哺乳動物的肌肉則通常為總體重的40-45%.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://natureinstitute.org/nature/sloth.htm|title=What Does It Mean to Be a Sloth?|website=natureinstitute.org|access-date=2017-06-29|archive-date=2019-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615043130/http://natureinstitute.org/nature/sloth.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。四肢上的長爪也能幫助樹懶輕鬆倒掛於樹枝上<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Mendel|first=Frank C.|date=1985-01-01|title=Use of Hands and Feet of Three-Toed Sloths (Bradypus variegatus) during Climbing and Terrestrial Locomotion|journal=Journal of Mammalogy|volume=66|issue=2|pages=359–366|doi=10.2307/1381249|jstor=1381249}}</ref>並在地表時讓樹懶得以爬行，畢竟牠們並沒有行走的能力。另外，三趾樹懶的前肢長度比後肢長50%<ref name="bri" />。

樹懶的移動速度十分緩慢，在樹上時平均速度約為每分鐘{{convert|4|m|ft}}，但遭遇掠食者時也能以每分鐘{{convert|4.5|m|ft}}的速度移動；若是在地面，則樹懶爬行的速度每分鐘可達{{convert|3|m|ft}}。牠們有時會坐在樹枝上，但多半仍以倒吊為主，即使是進食、睡覺或是生產，甚至死後屍體也會繼續掛在樹枝上。然而，樹懶在游泳時，速度可達每分鐘{{convert|13.5|m|ft}}<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Goffart|first=M.|date=1971|title=Function and Form in the sloth|url=|journal=International Series of Monographs in Pure and Applied Biology|volume=34|pages=94–95}}</ref>，藉由划動前肢，樹懶得以橫跨河流或島嶼<ref>{{Citation|last=BBC|title=Swimming sloth - Planet Earth II: Islands Preview - BBC One|date=2016-11-04|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ctutKTrf_NY|accessdate=2017-04-17|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221020030/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ctutKTrf_NY|dead-url=no}}</ref>。樹懶能使牠們很慢的新陳代謝進一步下降，將心跳速率減少至平常的1/3，這讓牠們得以於水中憋氣40分鐘<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Britton|first=S. W.|date=1941-01-01|title=Form and Function in the Sloth|journal=The Quarterly Review of Biology|volume=16|issue=1|pages=13–34|doi=10.1086/394620|jstor=2808832}}</ref>。

野生的褐喉三趾樹懶一天平均睡眠時間為9.6小時<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7396356.stm|title=Article "Sloth's Lazy Image 'A Myth'"|last=Briggs|first=Helen|date=2008-05-13|accessdate=2010-05-21|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101110716/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7396356.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。二趾樹懶為[[夜行性|夜行性]]<ref name="Eisenberg2000">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&pg=PA94|title=Mammals of the Neotropics, Volume 3: The Central Neotropics: Ecuador, Peru, Bolivia, Brazil|last=Eisenberg|first=John F.|author2=Redford, Kent H.|date=May 15, 2000|publisher=[[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]]|isbn=978-0-226-19542-1|location=|pages=624 (see pp. 94–95, 97)|oclc=493329394|access-date=2020-03-24|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919145623/https://books.google.com/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&pg=PA94|dead-url=no}}</ref>；三趾樹懶多半為夜行性，但白天有時也會活動，不過90%的時間都會待在原地<ref name="bri" />。

===食性===
樹懶寶寶透過舔母親唇上殘餘的植物組織來學習那些植物是否適合食用的<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-26734289|title=The woman who got 'slothified'|last=Venema|first=Vibeke|date=2014-04-04|work=BBC News|access-date=2017-12-01|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306065530/https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-26734289|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過所有樹懶都會以[[傘樹屬|傘樹屬]]的葉片為食。

二趾樹懶具有較多樣化的食性：包括[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]、腐肉、[[水果|水果]]、葉子與小型[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]，活動範圍可達 140 公頃。而三趾樹懶只以葉片為食，擁有哺乳動物中最慢的消化速度，終其一生可能都在同一棵樹上度過。樹葉難以消化且營養價值低，所以樹懶須透過巨大的胃與其內共生的[[細菌|細菌]]來慢慢消化這些樹葉。一隻飽食的樹懶<math>\frac{2}{3}</math>的體重來自於其胃囊中的內容物，而這些內容物需要至少一個月才能夠消化完全。

樹懶一週一次會爬下樹至地面進行[[排泄|排泄]]與[[排遺|排遺]]，在排出後更會將排泄物掩埋，在地面時樹懶十分容易遭到[[掠食者|掠食者]]的捕食。三趾樹懶會在固定的地點排便，而這項行為也能幫助維持樹懶毛上的獨特生態系<ref>Title:A syndrome of mutualism reinforces the lifestyle of a sloth
Authors:Jonathan N. Pauli, Jorge E. Mendoza, Shawn A. Steffan, Cayelan C.Carey, Paul J. Weimer and M. Zachariah Peery
Journal:Proceedings of the Royal Society B</ref>，而埋在樹旁的糞便，則能成為樹木的肥料<ref name="Community">{{cite web|last = Montgomery|first = Sy|title = Community Ecology of the Sloth|work = Cecropia: Supplemental Information|publisher = [[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica]]|url = http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/101053/cecropia/101053suppinfo/Supplemental-Information|accessdate = 2009-09-06|archive-date = 2009-05-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090524011902/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/101053/cecropia/101053suppinfo/Supplemental-Information|dead-url = no}}</ref>。最近研究顯示，樹懶蛾會將卵產在樹懶的糞便中，而幼蟲會以這些糞便為食，成年後這些蛾會在樹懶下幾次到地面排便時爬上樹懶的毛中棲息<ref name="gizmodo" />。

=== 繁殖 ===
褐喉與白喉三趾樹懶具有特定的繁殖季節，鬃毛三趾樹懶全年皆可繁殖，而侏三趾樹懶的繁殖則仍屬未知。三趾樹懶的[[妊娠期|妊娠期]]為六個月，二趾樹懶則為十二個月，一胎只會生下一隻幼崽，幼崽會與母親共同生活約五個月。在有些案例中，當幼崽墜落至地面時，母親會因為不願意爬下安全的樹而選擇遺棄幼崽，進而導致幼崽的喪生<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Soares|first=C. A.|last2=Carneiro|first2=R. S.|date=2002-05-01|title=Social behavior between mothers × young of sloths Bradypus variegatus SCHINZ, 1825 (Xenarthra: Bradypodidae)|journal=Brazilian Journal of Biology|volume=62|issue=2|pages=249–252|doi=10.1590/S1519-69842002000200008|pmid=12489397|issn=1519-6984}}</ref>。雌樹懶多半一年繁殖一次，但有時會因為行動遲緩找不到雄樹懶而失去繁殖的機會<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Pauli|first=Jonathan N.|last2=Peery|first2=M. Zachariah|date=2012-12-19|title=Unexpected Strong Polygyny in the Brown-Throated Three-Toed Sloth|journal=PLOS One|volume=7|issue=12|pages=e51389|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0051389|issn=1932-6203|pmc=3526605|pmid=23284687}}</ref>。樹懶並沒有明顯的[[兩性異形|兩性異形]]，有時動物園會收到被標示錯誤性別的個體<ref>{{cite news|title=Manly secret of non-mating sloth at London Zoo|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-11031719|website=BBC News|publisher=BBC|accessdate=30 April 2015|date=19 August 2010|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919145639/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-11031719|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Same-sex sloths dash Drusillas breeding plan|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-sussex-25233287|website=BBC News|publisher=BBC|accessdate=30 April 2015|date=5 December 2013|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205134604/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-sussex-25233287|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於缺乏長時的自然環境調查數據，野生二趾樹懶的平均壽命目前仍然未知<ref>{{cite web |title=About the Sloth |url=https://slothconservation.com/about-the-sloth/overview/ |website=Sloth Conservation Foundation |accessdate=31 October 2019 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116142251/https://slothconservation.com/about-the-sloth/overview/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；人工飼養的個體平均則約為16年，但有其中一隻飼養於[[史密森尼學會|史密森尼學會]][[美國國家動物園|美國國家動物園]]的二趾樹懶卻有活了49年的紀錄<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nationalzoo.si.edu/animals/southern-two-toed-sloth|title=Southern two-toed sloth|website=Smithsonian's National Zoo|language=en|access-date=2019-10-30|date=2016-04-25|archive-date=2019-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717065722/https://nationalzoo.si.edu/animals/southern-two-toed-sloth|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 天敵 ===
樹懶主要天敵之一是[[角鵰|角鵰]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Aguiar-Silva|first=F. Helena|last2=Sanaiotti|first2=Tânia M.|last3=Luz|first3=Benjamim B.|date=2014-03-01|title=Food Habits of the Harpy Eagle, a Top Predator from the Amazonian Rainforest Canopy|url=http://www.bioone.org/doi/abs/10.3356/JRR-13-00017.1|journal=Journal of Raptor Research|volume=48|issue=1|pages=24–35|doi=10.3356/JRR-13-00017.1|issn=0892-1016}}</ref>，可以無聲無息直接將樹懶抓起。另外[[美洲豹|美洲豹]]與[[豹貓|豹貓]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Moreno|first=Ricardo S.|last2=Kays|first2=Roland W.|last3=Samudio|first3=Rafael|date=2006-08-24|title=Competitive Release in Diets of Ocelot (Leopardus pardalis) and Puma (Puma concolor) after Jaguar (Panthera onca) Decline|url=https://academic.oup.com/jmammal/article/87/4/808/968843/Competitive-Release-in-Diets-of-Ocelot-Leopardus|journal=Journal of Mammalogy|volume=87|issue=4|pages=808–816|doi=10.1644/05-MAMM-A-360R2.1|issn=0022-2372|access-date=2018-10-26|archive-date=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518172404/https://academic.oup.com/jmammal/article/87/4/808/968843/Competitive-Release-in-Diets-of-Ocelot-Leopardus|dead-url=no}}</ref>也會獵捕樹懶。

== 棲息與分布地區==
[[File:Bradypus_pygmaeus.jpg|thumb]]
樹懶雖然只分布於中南美洲的熱帶雨林之中，牠們卻是當地十分繁盛的物種。在[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]的[[巴羅科羅拉多島|巴羅科羅拉多島]]上，樹懶估計佔了當地樹棲哺乳動物[[生物質|生物質量]]的70%<ref name="Eisenberg2000b">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&pg=PA96|title=Mammals of the Neotropics, Volume 3: The Central Neotropics: Ecuador, Peru, Bolivia, Brazil|last=Eisenberg|first=John F.|author2=Redford, Kent H.|date=May 15, 2000|publisher=[[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]]|isbn=978-0-226-19542-1|location=|pages=624 (see p. 96)|oclc=493329394|access-date=2020-01-07|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919145723/https://books.google.com/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&pg=PA96|dead-url=no}}</ref>。六個現存[[物種|物種]]之中，有四種為無危物種；棲息於巴西日益縮減的[[大西洋沿岸森林|大西洋沿岸森林]]的[[鬃毛三趾樹懶|鬃毛三趾樹懶]]，屬於易危物種<ref name="iucn B torquatus">{{Cite iucn | author = Chiarello, A. | author2 = Moraes-Barros, N. | last-author-amp = yes | title = ''Bradypus torquatus'' | volume = 2014 | page = e.T3036A47436575 | date = 2014 | doi = 10.2305/IUCN.UK.2014-1.RLTS.T3036A47436575.en }}</ref>，而棲息於離島上的[[侏三趾樹懶|侏三趾樹懶]]則為[[極危物種|極危物種]]。樹懶的低新陳代謝導致牠們只能生存於熱帶地區，且牠們必須透過曝曬於陽光下來提高體溫，類似於變溫動物的體溫調節系統<ref>{{cite news |last1=Dowling |first1=Stephen |title=Why do sloths move so slowly? |url=http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20190828-why-do-sloths-move-so-slowly |accessdate=2 September 2019 |work=BBC Future |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=29 August 2019 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912112900/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20190828-why-do-sloths-move-so-slowly |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 與人類之互動 ==
[[File:SlothDWA.jpg|thumb]]]]
在[[哥斯大黎加|哥斯大黎加]]，記錄到最主要樹懶的死因為被[[電線|電線]]電死以及遭到[[盜獵|盜獵]]。然而牠們的爪子大幅增加了盜獵的難度，因為即使遭到射殺，死掉的樹懶依然會因為牠們的長爪而繼續倒掛於樹上，不會掉落至地面。

人類會非法捕捉樹懶作為寵物販賣，但其實樹懶特殊的生活習性導致牠們並不適合一般民眾飼養<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/hottest-selling-animal-colombias-illegal-exotic-pet-trade/story?id=19172620|title=Sloths: Hottest-Selling Animal in Colombia's Illegal Pet Trade|last=News|first=A. B. C.|date=2013-05-29|website=ABC News|access-date=2017-12-02|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210221141/https://abcnews.go.com/International/hottest-selling-animal-colombias-illegal-exotic-pet-trade/story?id=19172620|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

蘇利南綠色遺產基金會（Green Heritage Fund Suriname）的創始人莫莉卡·普兒（Monique Pool）至今已拯救並釋放了超過600隻的樹懶、食蟻獸、犰狳以及豪豬<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/08/06/world/gallery/cnn-heroes-pool-sloths/index.html|title=When sloths are in trouble, she's the one to call|website=CNN|access-date=2017-12-01|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121184832/https://www.cnn.com/2015/08/06/world/gallery/cnn-heroes-pool-sloths/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{link-en|哥斯大黎加樹懶保育研究協會|The Sloth Institute Costa Rica}}主要的職務在於照顧、使樹懶恢復健康並將牠們釋放回野外<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theslothinstitutecostarica.org|title=The Sloth Institute website|access-date=2021-12-31|archive-date=2021-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331090928/http://www.theslothinstitutecostarica.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同樣位於哥斯大黎加的{{link-en|哥斯大黎加樹懶收容所|Sloth Sanctuary of Costa Rica}}主要也以照顧樹懶為主，並已成功釋放了約130隻個體回到野外<ref>{{Cite news| author = Sevcenko, Melanie| title = Sloth sanctuary nurtures animals back to health| work = Deutsche Welle| accessdate = 2013-04-18| date = 2013-04-17| url = http://www.dw.de/sloth-sanctuary-nurtures-animals-back-to-health/a-16750190| archive-date = 2015-05-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150513014722/http://www.dw.de/sloth-sanctuary-nurtures-animals-back-to-health/a-16750190| dead-url = no}}</ref>；然而，2016年五月的一篇報導中之前於該收容所工作的兩名獸醫指出，該收容所並沒有給予樹懶真正妥善的照護<ref>{{cite news | author = Schelling, Ameena | title = Famous Sloth Sanctuary Is A Nightmare For Animals, Ex-Workers Say | work = The Dodo | accessdate = 2016-05-20 | date = 2016-05-19 | url = https://www.thedodo.com/sloths-sanctuary-nightmare-1807794384.html | archive-date = 2021-01-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210118081459/https://www.thedodo.com/sloths-sanctuary-nightmare-1807794384.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

